@menuTypeId = <pega_el_id_del_tipo_de_menu>

### ─────────────────────────────
### MENU TYPES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar tipos de menú (STAFF)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar tipos de menú paginados
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar tipos de menú por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types?q=veget
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filtrar tipos de menú activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filtrar tipos de menú inactivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types?active=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar por nombre y estado activo
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types?q=menú&active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener tipo de menú por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types/one?menuTypeId={{menuTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear tipo de menú (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Menú Tradicional",
  "price": 10000
}

###

### Crear tipo de menú sin precio (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Menú Especial"
}

###

### Actualizar tipo de menú (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{menuTypeId}}",
  "name": "Vegetariano",
  "price": 9000,
  "active": true
}

###

### Quitar precio de tipo de menú (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{menuTypeId}}",
  "name": "Vegetariano",
  "price": null,
  "active": true
}

###

### Eliminar tipo de menú (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{menuTypeId}}"
}

###
